From 865ecae52d14431d0f5e3f03255b68d52cfd30ae Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Allsopp <david.allsopp@metastack.com>
Date: Sat, 19 Jul 2025 14:51:05 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Straighten out the INSTALL_* Makefile variables

Move various definitions around such that merged Makefile variables are
all in Makefile.common. Sanitise the names to be closer to
INSTALL_LIBDIR_subdirname.

(cherry picked from commit 35ca1e0ca9484973d352203e653ba597452034f9)

